headline: Argonne and partners celebrate Aurora supercomputer’s impact on science with AI and exascale power
summary: LEMONT, Ill., July 18, 2025--Aurora is revolutionizing how scientists use AI and simulation to tackle some of the most complex challenges in science and engineering.
